Detailed Description

Packet containing information about the edgenodes in a RoutingMap.

Packet contents:
PosSizeComment
X 4 bytes MapID.
X + 4 4 bytes Requested level.
X + 8 4 bytes User defined data.
X + 12 4 bytes 0x0000.
X + 16 4 bytes 0xffff.
X + 20 4 bytes MapID of overview map.
X + 24 4 bytes Number of bordering maps.
X + 32 4 bytes Number of external nodes on requested level.
X + 40 4 bytes Total number of external nodes.
X + 48 4 bytes * number of bordering maps MapID:s for bordering maps
X + 4*number of bordering maps (3 * 4 bytes) * number of external nodes ItemID, lat and lon for external nodes

Parameters:

borderMaps The maps to which this map has connections.
externalNodes The external node ID:s on this map.
lats The latitudes of the nodes.
lons The longitudes of the nodes.
distances Map containing map id in first and minimum distance from a destination in second.
totalNbrExt The total number of external nodes for the map on level 0.
